Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi, Katsuragi. It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the time you get this message,{\i0}\N{\i1}I've probably made life difficult for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry about that.{\i0}\N{\i1}And apologize to Ritchan for me, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't be asking favors,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I've been growing some flowers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you could water them for me,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'd appreciate it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji knows where they are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsuragi, the truth is with you.{\i0}\N{\i1}Keep going and don't look back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I see you again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll say the words that I couldn't{\i0}\N{\i1}say to you eight years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The silent phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,WORKING\NSORRY, DO NOT DISTURB
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"No unauthorized entry.\NYou come in, you die!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,NO UNAUTHORIZED ENTRY\NYOU COME IN, YOU DIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Asuka is planning\Nto stay away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She won't go to school,{\i0}\N{\i1}she won't go home...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She just sits there playing video games.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hikari?\N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm not being a bother, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to win, fighting in my Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worth anything anymore.\NNot to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it. I hate it all.\NI hate everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I hate most of all is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I just don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, I think you should do what\Nyou want. I won't tell you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I think you did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the poor thing died?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably. Cats don't live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll come home for a visit\Nwhen I find the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it’s been three years\Nsince I last visited Mom's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That cat died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for us to retrieve\Nthe Spear of Longinus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you employ it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eva series has not been completed\Nas per our plans yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave priority to the destruction\Nof the Angel. It was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unavoidable?" Your excuses need\Nto be a little more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of your recent actions\Nhave crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki, we're in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel is currently approaching.\NWe will continue this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming you are still\Nin command afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, do you intend to betray Seele?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there in 15. Send Unit 00\Nto the surface using No.32.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out Unit 02 to provide support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Commander Ikari\Nwill have final say over Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the authority\Nto lift its lockdown on my own. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have visual confirmation\Nof the Angel, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unit 00 away!{\i0}\N{\i1}Routing to intercept position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Unit 02 stand by at current position!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Launch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it. At the very least,\Nit can serve as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva-02, stand by for launch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At the controls again,\Nacting like I deserve to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when to give up, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Routing Unit 02 to Gate No.8.{\i0}\N{\i1}When egress point is determined, launch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah. Won't I just get in the way\Nif I go out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target closing. Has crossed{\i0}\N{\i1}Goura Absolute Defense Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target is holding above Owakudani.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's hovering in position and rotating.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Target's A.T. Field is still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where have you been?\N-I won't make excuses. Status?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Standoff situation is ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern cycling between Blue and Orange!\NIt's changing at regular intervals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-What does that mean?\N-The Magi show "Analysis Failure."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's not enough data\Nto formulate an answer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That shape isn't a fixed form,\Nwe can be sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei, we'll sit tight and see what it does.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rei! Return fire!\N-Too late! There's not enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Target in physical contact with Unit 00!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Unit 00's A.T. Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Deployed, but it's being\Ncorroded by the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Angel aggressively attempting\Na first contact? With Unit 00?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 00's biological components\Nare being corrupted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva-02, launch! Order her\Nto rescue Rei and provide cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Corruption by target is progressing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous. Over 5% of Unit 00\Nis now biologically melded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asuka, move up another 300,{\i0}\N{\i1}then raise your A.T. Field to maximum{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and fire your pallet gun{\i0}\N{\i1}into the target's rear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that? Eva-02, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out there! What's wrong, Asuka?\NUnit 02's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No go! Her synch rate\Nis in the single digits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't move... It won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a sitting duck up there!\NPull her back in! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The me inside the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I sense someone else who isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel?\NOne of the people we call Angels?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you become one with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm me. I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But you can't stop it.\NIt's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll share my heart with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll share my feelings with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in pain, aren't you?\NThere. Your heart is aching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aching? No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it. It's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lonely? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many of us.\NBut you're alone and you hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what we call "loneliness."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your heart you're feeling.\NIt's yours that is full of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,These are tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that's crying... is me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The lockdown on Unit 01 is hereby lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Launch it immediately.\N-Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? They didn't send him out\Nwhen I was the one who needed help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deploy your A.T. Field!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Rescue Rei! Hurry!{\i0}\N-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji! Engage with your Prog Knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurting me, Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what my heart wants?\NI want to be one with Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Her A.T. Field is inverting!\NCorruption spreading rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying to contain the Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Field is at maximum!\NUnable to sustain core!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei! Abandon the Eva! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. Without me,\Nthe A.T. Field will vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, are you going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The core is collapsing!\NIt's gone critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Target eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This operation is hereby concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stand down to condition one alert.\N-Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down to condition\Nyellow immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Unit 00's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No confirmation of entry plug ejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Begin search-and-rescue. Hurry.\N-Assuming there's anything {\i1}to{\i0} rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No component material of{\i0}\N{\i1}the 16th Angel has been found.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Level C contamination zone{\i0}\N{\i1}is spreading southwest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm designating this as top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve the plug.\NDispose of all associated parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we have defeated all\Nof the Angels up through the 16th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one of the Angels recorded in\NSeele's Dead Sea Scrolls now remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The promised time is nearly upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The road has been long,\Nand the sacrifices great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. First we lost the Spear\Nof Longinus, and now Eva-00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is more than enough reason\Nto dismiss Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When we returned Fuyutsuki unharmed,\Nsurely he understood our message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This calls for another sacrificial lamb.\NOne that Ikari cannot dismiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We also require someone\Nto know the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji? I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato, the tears aren't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad, but the tears just won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, all I can do for you\Nright now is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Ms. Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has to be feeling lonely...{\i0}\N{\i1}Maybe he's scared of women.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, what he's scared of{\i0}\N{\i1}is intimacy with others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pen Pen, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, now I get it. Anybody will do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one who was feeling lonely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the product of my despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and she remains the vessel\Nof all your hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's impossible\Nfor either of us to let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Paging Dr. Ugai.{\i0}\N{\i1}Dr. Ugai of Internal Medicine Dept. 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please contact{\i0}\N{\i1}Conference Room 2 immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,NEUROSURGERY NO.1, SURGERY NO.3\NSECOND FLOOR WARD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,RADIODIAGNOSTICS, X-RAY CHECK-IN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're alive, Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Father isn't here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NYou sacrificed Unit 00 to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I think I'm probably\Nthe third one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,AYANAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,These are tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be the first time\NI've seen them, but I feel like it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I... Am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Maintain status quo\Non the First Children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No new restrictions are necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for the Second and Third.\NJust keep them under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Keel and the others will\Nraise hell when they learn Rei is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sent the old men of Seele\Nsomething else to keep them occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We would prefer to proceed\Nin an amicable manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Subjecting you to further discomfort\Nor indignities is not our aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon,\Nbut I'm not the least bit ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong-willed woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why Ikari wants you at his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the person who offered you up\Nto us was none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He refused to allow\Nan interrogation of Unit 00's pilot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and presented you as her proxy, Dr. Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So now I'm Rei's replacement?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,WORKING\NSORRY, BUT DO NOT DISTURB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is part of the truth{\i0}\N{\i1}that you've been looking for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've sent it using 36 other methods,{\i0}\N{\i1}but those will probably never reach you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This capsule is the only way{\i0}\N{\i1}I know will work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is everything that I have.{\i0}\N{\i1}Use it as you see fit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The passcode is our first memory together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye. Take care of yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm through getting worked up\Nover a phone that won't ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have your heart inside me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we make the right choice\Nregarding Dr. Akagi's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She is different from Fuyutsuki.\NThe prudent course is to return her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She made great contributions to the Eva\Nseries. Let us use her a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, for the future of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelions... we will soon have\Neight of them at our disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Four more to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The obliteration of Tokyo-3\Nwill do much to advance the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a rush on the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Their completion will mark\Nthe arrival of the promised day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't talk, just listen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not under guard right now.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's safe to leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work. Not without my passcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Courtesy of Ryoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to let me see\Nthis place's secrets with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. But he'll be coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks just like Ayanami's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} Rei Ayanami's apartment.\NThis is where she was born and raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-It is?\N-Yes. She was born here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The imagery of this place\Nmust be deeply ingrained
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the water and light that\Nmake up Rei's deep psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Akagi, this isn't what I came to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Evas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The very first ones. They were failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Disposed of ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An Eva graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a dumping ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the place\Nwhere your mother disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not remember, but I'm sure\Nyou were watching when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment when your mother vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me that is where\Nthe Dummy Plugs come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, the Evas' Dummy Plugs are--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. These form the core\Nof the Dummy System.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their production plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just empty dummies.\NAnd simple spare parts for Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind stumbled across God.\NOverjoyed, we tried to possess it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we were punished.\NThat happened 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The God we were so excited about vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Undeterred, we then tried\Nto resurrect God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We made humans from Adam in God's image.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're people? They're human beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Evas are intrinsically soulless,\Nso we imbue them with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cobbled together\Nwith salvaged material.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only vessel that contained\Na soul was Rei. Only her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Only she was born with a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chamber of Guf was completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,None of these Rei-shaped things\Nhas a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just empty shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to smash them.\NBecause I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what you've done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. I've destroyed property.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These things aren't human.\NThey're human-shaped objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And I lost out even to those!\NI wasn't good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply thinking about him let me endure\Nany humiliation! Any outrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, that man... He never...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a fool! All along!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother and daughter alike,\Na matching pair of fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be doing me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that kind of thinking\Nthat makes you a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tragedy of those{\i0}\N{\i1}obsessed with the Evas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I any different?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.81,0:23:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.79,0:25:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The city the boy had been{\i0}\N{\i1}protecting is gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The friends he had{\i0}\N{\i1}grown close to have left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.05,0:25:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girls he was once attracted to{\i0}\N{\i1}have now turned to figures of dread.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.43,0:25:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the sun sets,{\i0}\N{\i1}a new boy smiles at Shinji,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.69,0:25:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who has lost the embodiments{\i0}\N{\i1}of his feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.11,0:25:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji melts before his smile, which seems{\i0}\N{\i1}to embrace and forgive his every sin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, a cruel fate has been{\i0}\N{\i1}arranged for the two of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.30,0:25:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "The Last Cometh"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.14,0:25:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Translator: Dan Kanemitsu\NSubtitle Editor: David Fleming
